OL,7,FThe Government has introduced a boiler
OL,8,Fupgrade scheme, giving homeowners
OL,9,Fgrants to replace gas boilers with
OL,10,Feco-friendly alternatives, such as heat
OL,11,Fpumps.
OL,13,FMinisters have said the grant will make
OL,14,Fheat pumps cost a similar amount to gas
OL,15,Fboilers.
